---
import { getEntry } from 'astro:content';
import ProjectHero from '../../components/ProjectHero.astro';
import ProjectLayout from '../../layouts/ProjectLayout.astro';
import ColsLeft from '../../components/rows/ColsLeft.astro';
import CustomImage from '../../components/CustomImage.astro';
import Flex from '../../components/rows/Flex.astro';
import ColsRight from '../../components/rows/ColsRight.astro';

const project = await getEntry('projects', 'dev-ops');
---

<ProjectLayout>
  <ProjectHero
    title={project.data.title}
    year={project.data.year}
    subtitle={project.data.subtitle}
    category={project.data.category}
    cover={project.data.cover}
  />

  <ColsLeft title="ci/cd pipelines">
    <div slot="col1">
      <h3>Automated Development Operations</h3>

      <p>
                Built comprehensive CI/CD pipelines and development automation that streamlined deployment processes, improved code quality, and enhanced developer productivity across multiple projects.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Pipeline Achievements:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Store Pipeline</strong> - Comprehensive test runner with code coverage</li>
        <li><strong>Local Development Automation</strong> - One-command WordPress setup</li>
        <li><strong>Scheduled Pipelines</strong> - Automated review import processes</li>
        <li><strong>Database Management</strong> - Backup, restore, and import automation</li>
        <li><strong>Dependency Management</strong> - Automated installation and configuration</li>
      </ul>
    </div>

    <CustomImage
      slot="col2"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-cover.png')}
      alt="CI/CD Pipeline Architecture"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />

    <Flex slot="col2">
      <CustomImage
        src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-main-window.jpg')}
        alt="Automated Testing"
        width={1920}
        height={1200}
      />

      <CustomImage
        src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/cloud-infrastructure.svg')}
        alt="Code Coverage Reports"
        width={1920}
        height={1200}
      />
    </Flex>
  </ColsLeft>

  <ColsRight title="local development">
    <div slot="col2">
      <h3>One-Command Setup</h3>

      <p>
                Created a revolutionary local development setup that automated the entire WordPress project initialization process, dramatically reducing setup time from hours to minutes.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Automation Features:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Database Management</strong> - Automated pull of recent backups</li>
        <li><strong>Data Refresh</strong> - Clean local data deletion and import</li>
        <li><strong>Dependency Installation</strong> - Automated package management</li>
        <li><strong>Configuration Setup</strong> - Environment-specific settings</li>
        <li><strong>Single Command</strong> - Complete WordPress project ready to work</li>
        <li><strong>Developer Experience</strong> - Eliminated manual setup complexity</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
                This automation transformed the developer onboarding experience and made switching between projects seamless and efficient.
      </p>
    </div>

    <CustomImage
      slot="col1"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-cover.png')}
      alt="Local Development Setup"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />

    <CustomImage
      slot="col1"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-main-window.jpg')}
      alt="WordPress Automation"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />
  </ColsRight>

  <ColsLeft title="containerization">
    <div slot="col1">
      <h3>Docker & Database Optimization</h3>

      <p>
                Implemented comprehensive containerization strategies and database optimization techniques to ensure consistent development environments and optimal performance.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Infrastructure Solutions:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li><strong>Docker Containers</strong> - MERN apps and WordPress instances</li>
        <li><strong>MySQL Optimization</strong> - Views, stored procedures, and indexing</li>
        <li><strong>Environment Consistency</strong> - Containerized development setups</li>
        <li><strong>Performance Tuning</strong> - Database query optimization</li>
        <li><strong>Scalable Architecture</strong> - Multi-project container orchestration</li>
        <li><strong>Development Standardization</strong> - Consistent tooling across teams</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
                These containerization and optimization strategies provided reliable, performant development environments that could be easily replicated and maintained across the entire engineering team.
      </p>
    </div>

    <CustomImage
      slot="col2"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/cloud-infrastructure.svg')}
      alt="Docker Containerization"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />
  </ColsLeft>

  <ColsRight title="automation impact">
    <div slot="col2">
      <h3>Development Efficiency Revolution</h3>

      <p>
                The DevOps automation initiatives fundamentally transformed the development workflow, eliminating manual processes and enabling developers to focus on building features rather than managing infrastructure.
      </p>

      <p>
        <strong>Business Impact:</strong>
      </p>
      <ul>
        <li>Reduced project setup time from hours to minutes</li>
        <li>Eliminated manual database management overhead</li>
        <li>Increased deployment confidence through automated testing</li>
        <li>Standardized development environments across all projects</li>
        <li>Improved code quality through automated pipeline checks</li>
        <li>Enhanced developer productivity and satisfaction</li>
      </ul>

      <p>
                This comprehensive DevOps approach created a foundation for rapid, reliable software development and deployment across the entire organization.
      </p>
    </div>

    <CustomImage
      slot="col1"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-cover.png')}
      alt="DevOps Impact Metrics"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />

    <CustomImage
      slot="col1"
      src={import('../../assets/projects/hi-design/hi-design-main-window.jpg')}
      alt="Development Efficiency"
      width={1920}
      height={1200}
    />
  </ColsRight>
</ProjectLayout>
